The room is very inorganic.[p]
While shining my flashlight about, I move through the room and eventually discover a grate in the floor.[p]
From between the bars in the grate, I can see a staircase that leads to a lower floor.[p]
The grate makes a 'clunk' sound as I open it. [p]
It is quite heavy.[p]
Even though I am sure of my strength, I do not believe that I could pick it up.[p]
After opening the grate enough so that I can pass through it, I gently place one foot on the staircase that has appeared.[p]


